.\" termin.al-name: logout
.\" termin.al-usage: logout
.\" termin.al-summary: End the authenticated session.
.TH LOGOUT 1 "" "termin.al" "termin.al Manual"
.ftr B R
.ftr I R
.ftr BI R
.SH NAME
logout \- End the authenticated session.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
logout
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
Ends the protected browser session and removes owner, GitHub-viewer and shared-CV capabilities. Open CV presentation state is discarded. Editor drafts are not changed.
.SH OUTPUT
Prints
.BR "Logged out."
on success.
.SH FAILURES
Arguments are rejected. Session, origin or request-forgery failures report
.BR "Authentication failed." .
.SH NOTES
The offline demo clears only its synthetic in-memory capability state.
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
$ logout
.fi
.SH SEE ALSO
login(1), whoami(1), cv(1)
